Final wave of the Set Action dialog audit: the "delete" action now surfaces a confirmation modal showing the matched count and a human-readable pattern summary before emitting (Cancel is the default Esc target so a misfired Enter cannot fire a bulk delete; other actions emit immediately unchanged), and a new "Test against:" input above the preview list lets users try a single hand-typed string against the current regex with live ✓/✗ feedback and match-position info — without adding the string to their actual file collection (#350).
